      "id": "PopularPost8455",
      "post_content": "I agree with the people who think that this works great in an Esper zombie deck. Sure, the only other white zombie card is [Tidehollow Sculler](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tidehollow Sculler), but even the sculler and covenant are a good enough reason to build an esper zombie deck. But what the covenant really excels with is [Mind Funeral](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Funeral). Mill an entire chunk of your opponents library and then watch them cry as you (in addition to ruining their deck) summon of lifelink zombies. and when their played with one of the zombie lords such as [Death Baron](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death Baron) or [Lord of the Undead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Lord of the Undead), then victory is in your favor.",
