      "id": "PopularPost5748",
      "post_content": "im not sure how i feel about how this block has thrown a zombie into every colour combination out there. Obviously the majortiy of zombies in this block are blue/black/red. That makes it difficult to play this card and [tidehollow sculler](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=tidehollow sculler) (both great cards that i wish were blue instead).\n  \nThankfully there are cards like rupture spire, or the [grixis illusionist](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=grixis illusionist), that will make this card playable potentially even without white mana. It's just too bad i have to put filler cards in to make this card more easily playable.\n  \nCan anyone think of a way to get this card into play easily with a Grixis colour scheme deck?",
      "posted_by": "Cenelder",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost5748\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">im not sure how i feel about how this block has thrown a zombie into every colour combination out there.  Obviously the majortiy of zombies in this block are blue/black/red.  That makes it difficult to play this card and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"tidehollow sculler\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=tidehollow sculler\">tidehollow sculler</a> (both great cards that i wish were blue instead).  \r<br/>Thankfully there are cards like rupture spire, or the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"grixis illusionist\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=grixis illusionist\">grixis illusionist</a>, that will make this card playable potentially even without white mana.  It's just too bad i have to put filler cards in to make this card more easily playable.\r<br/>Can anyone think of a way to get this card into play easily with a Grixis colour scheme deck?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '5748'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy1063\">Cenelder</span>\r\n                                (4/30/2009 9:10:06 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                      