      "id": "PopularPost8617",
      "post_content": "It actually doesn't go well with [Unscythe, Killer of Kings](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unscythe, Killer of Kings). Unless you plan to target yourself with Covenant, Unscythe is going to remove all of the prospective zombies. I guess you could use it after all of your Covenants, but it just doesn't seem worth it.  \n  \n[Orzhov Basilica](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Orzhov Basilica) works pretty well to get this down, or you can use the Esper obelisk or triple land.",
